  "bodyHtml": "<div class=\"is-container-in\">\n<div class=\"remote-row clearfix\">\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<h3 class=\"big-one-two\"><span style=\"font-size:28px;\">2021 AMC10A/12A</span><span style=\"font-size:26px;\">難題解析 宗翰老師主講</span><small></small></h3>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><span style=\"font-size:18px;\">Youtube連結:<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/f9LvM7LEcPs?fbclid=IwAR2Gd_G_142DK8jH-ZwVwDpc6abvckcAqFP4E_rA4RhuEndlZshhBDdrvhw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\" role=\"link\" tabindex=\"0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/f9LvM7LEcPs</a><br />\n宗翰老師特別針對這次2021 AMC10A/12A深水區的難題做詳細解析，並且應孩子們的要求，公開2/6當天網課講座影片，讓大家一起學習，歡迎孩子們一起來看，考完試也要確實訂正才能進步喔！<br />\n<br />\n2/6當天線上講座收款已全數捐出喜憨兒基金會幫助需要幫助的孩子們，感謝當天一起參與的爸爸媽媽和孩子們和我們一起做公益！(收據請見底下留言)</span></p>\n\n<p class=\"normal-txt\"><u style=\"color: rgb(0, 158, 145); font-size: 20px;\"><a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/764632944489393/\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/695697124716309/permalink/764632944489393/</a></u></p>\n</div>\n\n<div class=\"column half\">\n<div class=\"embed-responsive embed-responsive-4by3\"><iframe allowfullscreen=\"\" frameborder=\"0\" height=\"315\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/f9LvM7LEcPs?rel=0\" width=\"100%\"></iframe></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
